      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<h2>Opening the Scene App</h2><p>Shortcut: Ctl+J or Journal Notes -&gt; Scene Tags</p><img src=\"systems/mist-engine-fvtt/assets/screenshots/opening_scene_app.jpg\" /><p></p><h2>Adding Tags &amp; Statuses from Challenges As Dice Roll Modifiers</h2><p>Click on a tag or status in the Tags &amp; Status section from a challenge on the left side to add them as dice roll modifiers.</p><img src=\"systems/mist-engine-fvtt/assets/screenshots/add_tags_status_from_challenge.jpg\" /><p></p><h2>Drag'N'Drop of Tags &amp; Statuses from a challenge to the scene app or character</h2><p>You can drag'n'drop tags &amp; statuses from the Threats &amp; Consequences of  challenge to the scene app</p>"
