    {
      "sort": 200000,
      "name": "Fellowship Themebooks",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "zLZwDJ0ul7XRcL0Q",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>Fellowship Themebooks are special. They are technically a seperate actor which all users from the fellowship have ownership.</p><p></p><h2>1. Create an actor of the type \"Fellowship Themecard\"</h2><img src=\"systems/mist-engine-fvtt/assets/screenshots/fellowshio_themecard_creation.jpg\" /><p></p><h2>2. Give all fellowship characters(users) ownership to the fellowship themecard (actor)</h2><img src=\"systems/mist-engine-fvtt/assets/screenshots/configure_ownership_of_fellowship.jpg\" /><p></p><h2>3 Assign characters to their corresponding user</h2><p>Do not forget to assign the characters to their corresponding users. Do NOT assign the fellowship themecard actor, just the character of the user.</p><img src=\"systems/mist-engine-fvtt/assets/screenshots/user_configuration_1.jpg\" /><p></p><img src=\"systems/mist-engine-fvtt/assets/screenshots/user_configuration_2.jpg\" /><p>After setting up the character assignment and after a reload / or relogin of the users, they will see the fellowship themecard in their charactersheet.</p>"
      },
